title: Weekend Decisions In The Moment
itunes:title: Weekend Decisions In The Moment
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Today's episode is the second of our three part series on weekends. In this episode we talk about how to handle quick changes in the plan and what to do when you catch yourself OFF plan.

We all have moments. But you get to decide what feeling to attach to it. You also get to decide how you will think about the next meal.
